// // Field storing the integer value which the threads are racing to update.
// // Initially 0, but can be updated to a {positive, negative} value depending
// // on which thread wins the race.
// field value: Int
// // Field set after the value is read, signalling that the interferer
// // thread must stop interfering.
// field value_is_read: Bool
// // Field storing the "flag", which allows the race to be resolved.
// field flag:  Bool
// // Field determining whether or not the update is done and can now
// // be retreived
